(51933, 109969, 0, 1, 'Answer me,Please.', '當世界的聲音只剩下繁忙的嘈雜\r\n我們只是想得到對方的一點慰藉\r\n\r\n他/她\r\n沒能回答你\r\n因為正忙於自己的另一個世界\r\n\r\n當你聲嘶力竭的大喊著「回答我」\r\n沒有人可以回答你\r\n\r\n才發現不是世界改變了感情\r\n是我們選擇了接受了自己這樣\r\n\r\n更孤獨的改變。', '2012-07-25 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 1, 7, 'Answer me', '', 113, '', '蘇曉花', '蘇曉花', '蘇曉花', '蘇曉花音樂工作室', '', 0, 0, 0, '2012-07-25 16:52:46', '2015-03-12 13:54:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(51934, 153171, 0, 1, 'We''ll fight this fight (Demo)', '', '2012-07-25 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, 'We''ll fight this fight forever.\n我們會抗爭到底\nWe''ll clench our own fist.\n用我們緊握的雙拳\nEnemy at the gate.\n敵人就在眼前\nWaiting for your last breathing.\n等待你最後一次的呼吸\n\nWe''ll fight this fight forever.\n我們會抗爭到底\nWe''ll clench our own fist.\n用我們緊握的雙拳\nWho will stand on my side.\n夥伴或是敵人\nIts time to make your mind.\n你現在就得做出抉擇\n\nWhen the raindrops falling on my eyes.\n當雨水模糊我的雙眼\nI still can see the view inside me.\n我依然可以看見心中的景象\nWhen the storm cover up all the voice.\n即使風暴會蓋過所有的聲音\nI''ll still be shouting out loud.\n我依然會更用力的吶喊\n\nWe''ll fight this fight forever.\n我們會抗爭到底\nWe''ll clench our own fist.\n用我們緊握的雙拳\nThey call me a traitor.\n他們說我是背叛者\nI getting stronger...\n所以我不斷的努力茁壯\nto prove they are fucking liar...\n去證明他們是該死的騙子\n\nWe''ll fight this fight forever.\n我們會抗爭到底\nWe''ll clench our own fist.\n用我們緊握的雙拳\nTrust yourself...\n相信你自己\nDont be afraid...\n不要害怕\nPain will make your way to me.\n疼痛只是讓我們更加的堅信\n\nWhen the raindrops falling on my eyes.\n當雨水模糊我的雙眼\nI still can see the view inside me.\n我依然可以看見心中的景象\nWhen the storm cover up all the voice.\n即使風暴會蓋過所有的聲音\nI''ll still be shouting out loud.\n我依然會更用力的吶喊\n\nCan you hear me call?\n你能聽見我的呼喚嗎？\nCan you feel my tired mind?\n你能感受到我內心的疲憊嗎？\nIt fade away in the long past memory....\n它們早就是我們過去的回憶了...', '', 257, '', 'R.E.C.', 'R.E.C. & 林怡良', 'R.E.C.', '', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-07-25 19:22:20', '2015-03-12 13:54:37', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(51935, 153171, 0, 1, 'So Far Away [Demo]', '我們都在現實與回憶中，\r\n追逐著逐漸模糊的背影，\r\n但這之間的距離並沒有縮短，\r\n反而越來越遙遠。', '2012-07-25 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 7, '血液在我身體燃燒　麻痺\r\n麻痺了自己　我彷彿快要窒息\r\n我抗拒不了回憶　沉默不語\r\n是為了想停止再嘆息\r\n\r\nI cant take it no more.\r\nWhen my dream and my faith...\r\nWhen I try to ran away...\r\nI hear your voice with me.\r\nPlease give me a sign....\r\n\r\nCause You''re so far away.\r\nI cant feel it.\r\nDont go away.\r\nStay with me...\r\nStay with me....\r\n\r\nIts time...Time to for my test.\r\nThis time...I nerver ever quiet.\r\nIt just a test for me.\r\nIt just a test for my load.\r\n\r\nI hear your voice with me...\r\nPlease give me a sign.\r\n\r\nCause You''re so far away.\r\nI cant feel it.\r\nDont go away.\r\nStay with me...\r\n\r\nSo I keep....driving.....', '', 347, '', 'R.E.C.', 'R.E.C.', 'R.E.C.', '', '', 0, 1, 1, '2012-07-25 19:29:38', '2013-10-07 17:22:08', '2013-06-30 13:36:20'),
